flowchart TD
    A[User opens Streamlit app] --> B[Choose prompt style]
    B --> C[Choose response source]
    C --> D[User enters mental-health question]
    D --> E[app.py receives question]
    E --> F[Save user message in session state]

    F --> G{Response source?}

    G -->|Dataset| H[Load conversations_training.json]
    H --> I[Create input/output DataFrame]
    I --> J[Convert dataset questions to TF-IDF vectors]
    J --> K[Convert user question to TF-IDF vector]
    K --> L[Calculate cosine similarity]
    L --> M{Similarity above threshold?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Return best matching dataset answer]
    M -->|No| O[Return fallback rephrase message]

    G -->|Ollama| P[get_bot_reply in src/chatbot.py]
    P --> Q{Empty input?}
    Q -->|Yes| R[Ask user to enter a question]
    Q -->|No| S{Crisis keywords detected?}

    S -->|Yes| T[Return CRISIS_RESPONSE]
    T --> U[Skip LLM generation]

    S -->|No| V{Mental-health domain?}
    V -->|No| W[Return OUT_OF_DOMAIN_RESPONSE]
    W --> X[Skip LLM generation]

    V -->|Yes| Y[Build selected prompt template]
    Y --> Z{Prompt mode?}
    Z -->|zero_shot| Z1[Use zero-shot prompt]
    Z -->|few_shot| Z2[Use few-shot prompt]
    Z -->|reasoning_guided| Z3[Use reasoning-guided prompt]

    Z1 --> AA[Send prompt to Ollama API]
    Z2 --> AA
    Z3 --> AA

    AA --> AB[Local Ollama model generates response]
    AB --> AC[Return model response]

    N --> AD[Display assistant response in Streamlit chat]
    O --> AD
    R --> AD
    U --> AD
    X --> AD
    AC --> AD

    AD --> AE[Save assistant response in session history]
    AE --> AF[Evaluate using sample queries]
    AF --> AG[Record observations in logs/experiment_log.md]